Class SoftwareBinary

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.arc.pds.xml.generated.SoftwareBinary

  • public class SoftwareBinary
extends java.lang.Object
    The Software Binary class provides a description of a software code that is stored as a compiled binary file.
